{"tid":739991,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"MacBook Pro 大更新 **外置 GPU 也正式上架 Apple Store 了。","createTime":"2018-07-12T13:35:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T21:14:06.000Z","uid":19208,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6b01d40b60a6ee149a4e3efc901758c5aa5234e2","tid":739991,"uid":19208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:35:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>MacBook Pro 大更新：搭載更快處理器、更大電池、更好看的螢幕</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><a href=\"https://www.apple.com/hk/macbook-pro/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fmacbook-pro%2F&d=uJLkQzv8w54hPBWmsmKDI4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=e2ddcbda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.apple.com/hk/macbook-pro/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><a href=\"https://www.apple.com/hk-zh/shop/product/HM8Y2B/A/blackmagic-egpu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com%2Fhk-zh%2Fshop%2Fproduct%2FHM8Y2B%2FA%2Fblackmagic-egpu&d=uJLkQzv8w54hPBWmsmKDI4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=535b8bae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.apple.com/hk-zh/shop/product/HM8Y2B/A/blackmagic-egpu</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/56fe89780b25eadaef887398d49bbb9d/206521568/MBP_13%2Band%2B15%2Bhero-PRINT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.aolcdn.com%2Fhss%2Fstorage%2Fmidas%2F56fe89780b25eadaef887398d49bbb9d%2F206521568%2FMBP_13%252Band%252B15%252Bhero-PRINT.png&h=ef89bef9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n引頸以待的 MacBook Pro 更新也終於來臨了，雖然外形不變，但新 13 吋和 15 吋 MacBook Pro 的內在都幾乎換上新配置，讓新版本的用戶有著不一樣的使用體驗。<br />\n<br />\n15 吋版本的 MacBook Pro 將會可選用最高 Intel 第八代 i7 或 i9 的六核心處理器、最高 32GB DDR4 RAM、4TB 儲存空間，獨顯的部分更是升級至 4GB VRAM 的 AMD Radeon Pro GPU；13 吋版本則可選 Intel 第八代四核心的 i5 或 i7 處理器，儲存空間也可選最高 2TB 之大，圖像處理器則為擁有 128MB eDRAM 的 Iris Plus 655。針對有更高圖像處理需要的用家，Apple 也正式上架來自 Blackmagic 的外置 GPU 配件，699 美元 / HK$6,498 / NT$25,590 的版本將搭載一片有 8GB GDDR5 RAM 的 AMD Radeon Pro 580，機身上將會有兩個 Thunderbolt 3 插孔、四個 USB 3.0 以及一個 HDMI 2.0 輸出，同時其 85W 電源輸入也可以同時為 Macbook 提供電力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/d07fcede9bd74d14be78f6d3541c26dc/206520339/MBP_3D_Rendering_Performance_13-PRINT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.aolcdn.com%2Fhss%2Fstorage%2Fmidas%2Fd07fcede9bd74d14be78f6d3541c26dc%2F206520339%2FMBP_3D_Rendering_Performance_13-PRINT.png&h=04db7b7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新版本 MacBook Pro 的螢幕尺寸雖然沒有變動，但卻起用了新的面板，讓 iPad Pro 的 True Tone 技術加入至 MacBook Pro 之上，更妙的是連 Touch Bar 也支援這自適應色溫功能呢。另外，首現於 iMac Pro 的 T2 安全晶片也有放到新的 MacBook Pro 裡，負責系統的各元件，包括系統管理控制器。當然，這晶片支援全時喚時的能力，使用者可以隨時召喚 Siri 助手。<br />\n<br />\n新設計 MacBook 系列最被人垢病的鍵盤部分，Apple 在這次的新版本 MacBook Pro 中也有更新。據 Apple 的介紹指這鍵盤會比較安靜，但主站編輯在短暫的動手玩時間裡卻感覺沒有太大的改變，畢竟原來的蝴蝶腳鍵盤也不算特別吵耳就是了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/d98586715dff0b711daaadc73018c7cf/206520318/180711_MacBookPro_NewYorkCity_BK_41579.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.aolcdn.com%2Fhss%2Fstorage%2Fmidas%2Fd98586715dff0b711daaadc73018c7cf%2F206520318%2F180711_MacBookPro_NewYorkCity_BK_41579.JPG&h=2254c39b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就有如 iMac Pro 和新 iPad 都有分別找來開發者和教師提供意見的做法，Apple 這次為了這新的 MacBook Pro，也選定了攝影師、音樂家、程序員三個專業人士的群體來預先體驗。他們分享了使用搭載 i9 處理器 + 4TB SSD 版本的 MBP 後的工作流程，用以證明 Apple 是透過真實用家的回饋來設計新產品。<br />\n<br />\n具備 Touch Bar 和 Touch ID 的新版本的 MacBook Pro 13 吋的定價為 HK$14,388 / NT$57,900 起；15 吋的定價為 HK$18,988 / NT$77,900 起。"},{"pid":"b943e81ed955fba3de18964e98066b3fa5fb37b0","tid":739991,"uid":19208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://store.storeimages.cdn-apple.com/8755/as-images.apple.com/is/image/AppleInc/aos/published/images/H/M8/HM8Y2/HM8Y2?wid=1144&amp;hei=1144&amp;fmt=jpeg&amp;qlt=80&amp;op_usm=0.5%2C0.5&amp;.v=1529949316965\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.storeimages.cdn-apple.com%2F8755%2Fas-images.apple.com%2Fis%2Fimage%2FAppleInc%2Faos%2Fpublished%2Fimages%2FH%2FM8%2FHM8Y2%2FHM8Y2%3Fwid%3D1144%26hei%3D1144%26fmt%3Djpeg%26qlt%3D80%26op_usm%3D0.5%252C0.5%26.v%3D1529949316965&h=6a21c280&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://store.storeimages.cdn-apple.com/8755/as-images.apple.com/is/image/AppleInc/aos/published/images/H/M8/HM8Y2/HM8Y2_AV3?wid=1144&amp;hei=1144&amp;fmt=jpeg&amp;qlt=80&amp;op_usm=0.5%2C0.5&amp;.v=1529949318285\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.storeimages.cdn-apple.com%2F8755%2Fas-images.apple.com%2Fis%2Fimage%2FAppleInc%2Faos%2Fpublished%2Fimages%2FH%2FM8%2FHM8Y2%2FHM8Y2_AV3%3Fwid%3D1144%26hei%3D1144%26fmt%3Djpeg%26qlt%3D80%26op_usm%3D0.5%252C0.5%26.v%3D1529949318285&h=5091a165&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>產品資訊</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>概要</strong><br />\nBlackmagic eGPU 把桌面電腦級的圖像處理效能帶到你的 MacBook Pro。採用 Radeon Pro 580 圖像處理器，Blackmagic eGPU 讓任何配備 Thunderbolt 3 連接埠的 Mac 化身成威力強大的圖像處理中心。玩遊戲順暢無比，在需要大量圖像處理的專業 app 上工作，流程明顯加快，更可讓你體驗 VR 樂趣甚至製作內容。內置 I/O 連接可同時驅動一部 Thunderbolt 3 顯示器、支援多種配件，並為你的 MacBook Pro 充電。<br />\n<br />\n以 Blackmagic eGPU 配合擁有絢麗解像度、畫質完美的 LG UltraFine 5K 顯示器，體驗終極強大的 Mac 設定。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>特色重點</strong><br />\n兼容配備 Thunderbolt 3 連接埠的 Mac<br />\n<br />\nRadeon Pro 580 圖像處理器配備 8GB GDDR5 記憶體<br />\n<br />\n兩個 Thunderbolt 3 連接埠<br />\n<br />\n四個 USB 3 連接埠<br />\n<br />\n一個 HDMI 2.0 連接埠<br />\n<br />\n85W 電力傳輸<br />\n<br />\n<strong>包裝盒內容</strong><br />\nBlackmagic eGPU<br />\n<br />\nThunderbolt 3 連接線 (0.5 米)"},{"pid":"f48bd141c109aa6375311b36006a9b5039406606","tid":739991,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T13:41:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda11310743e9f1bc8b61018027379ebea2dcb81","tid":739991,"uid":5499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T14:06:56.000Z","msg":"幾時cpu 都外置埋？"},{"pid":"8b85745345663381403661fdefc1b287256860f8","tid":739991,"uid":185935,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"dda11310743e9f1bc8b61018027379ebea2dcb81","tid":739991,"uid":5499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T14:06:56.000Z","msg":"幾時cpu 都外置埋？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T14:13:34.000Z","msg":"拆咗個殼，所有嘢都變外置～"},{"pid":"9e9858d06c6401a9ec2b348ec5cc75a28049ea7a","tid":739991,"uid":8687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T20:34:31.000Z","msg":"i9 32G ram 1tb SSD 要三皮幾野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1bf0be162dc6fb273057717d2fb8eb41182be94","tid":739991,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T21:08:06.000Z","msg":"DDR 5 同4TB ssd聽落係幾好..但係會唔會好L嘈個風線（仲要外置顯）熱到bbq?<br />\n<br />\n利申2016買16GB ram i7 MacBook Pro 玩minecraft 個風線都可以熱到9叫"},{"pid":"aa856ee35b94a4aae026af719309bec7afd69a02","tid":739991,"uid":135867,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9e9858d06c6401a9ec2b348ec5cc75a28049ea7a","tid":739991,"uid":8687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T20:34:31.000Z","msg":"i9 32G ram 1tb SSD 要三皮幾野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T21:14:06.000Z","msg":"一皮硬件一皮軟體一皮生活態度"}]}